    <p>DVLCube (www.dvlcube.com) provides developer utilities and tools. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our website and services.</p>

    <h5>1. Information We Collect</h5>
    
    <h6>1.1 Automatically Collected Information</h6>
    <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain technical information:</p>
