      <li>Correction of inaccurate information</li>
      <li>Deletion of your information</li>
      <li>Objection to processing of your information</li>
      <li>Data portability</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided below.</p>

    <h5>8. Children's Privacy</h5>
    <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.</p>

    <h5>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h5>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.</p>

